331
00:19:29,760 --> 00:19:30,400
Yes.

332
00:19:30,940 --> 00:19:35,500
♪The silent youth♪

333
00:19:36,220 --> 00:19:40,540
♪Tomorrow will have the answer♪

334
00:19:41,260 --> 00:19:46,300
♪The box will be full of memories♪

335
00:19:47,380 --> 00:19:52,540
