381
00:22:34,600 --> 00:22:36,000
I took Xu Guo Xiang's dirty money

382
00:22:36,000 --> 00:22:37,360
that can't be known by the public.

383
00:22:38,440 --> 00:22:39,200
He set up a company

384
00:22:39,360 --> 00:22:40,080
in my name

385
00:22:40,120 --> 00:22:41,080
