386
00:22:41,680 --> 00:22:42,600
to help him

387
00:22:42,680 --> 00:22:43,840
launder money from unknown sources.

388
00:22:45,960 --> 00:22:46,520
Since he's

389
00:22:46,600 --> 00:22:47,400
treating me this way,

390
00:22:47,560 --> 00:22:48,920
I'll just go along with it

391
00:22:49,800 --> 00:22:51,200
