408
00:25:03,600 --> 00:25:05,280
I just want you to be safe.

409
00:25:09,560 --> 00:25:11,440
To wait for death?

410
00:25:18,480 --> 00:25:19,680
Qing Zi said

411
00:25:20,920 --> 00:25:21,920
at least

412
00:25:22,080 --> 00:25:23,640
