413
00:25:24,720 --> 00:25:27,320
Maybe during this period of time,

414
00:25:27,480 --> 00:25:29,120
other labs might come up

415
00:25:29,320 --> 00:25:30,480
with new solutions.

416
00:25:31,200 --> 00:25:32,520
Look on the bright side.

417
00:25:33,840 --> 00:25:35,800
Since Qing Zi has told you everything,

418
00:25:36,840 --> 00:25:38,400
I'm sure you know

419
00:25:40,080 --> 00:25:42,160
it will not last more than a year

420
00:25:42,680 --> 00:25:43,880
after the safe mode is activated.

421
00:25:48,280 --> 00:25:50,320
I don't want to live like a machine,

422
00:25:51,480 --> 00:25:53,400
being unable to feel happiness or pain,

423
00:25:54,320 --> 00:25:55,960
or have the feeling of loving someone
and being loved.

424
00:25:58,360 --> 00:26:00,240
I don't want to live a life

425
00:26:01,240 --> 00:26:02,680
without hope

426
00:26:03,440 --> 00:26:04,800
and emotion like before.

427
00:26:06,160 --> 00:26:07,080
Also,

428
00:26:08,360 --> 00:26:09,840
